{"tid":1253731,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"又話華為收皮嘅？點解佢仲有新機新cpu出？？","createTime":"2019-06-23T17:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T10:22:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e95cb199d608c6e4d8f263121a2edfe90471ff16","tid":1253731,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"華為發表 Nova 5：首配 Kirin 810 效能勁過旗艦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m.ringhk.com/editor/news2018/20190621_nova5_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2018%2F20190621_nova5_01.jpg&h=b54e371d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然遭受美國封殺，但仍然無阻華為推新機的計劃。剛剛華為就在中國發表 Nova 5，搭載 48MP 四鏡頭的同時，更搶先採用新一代 Kirin 810 處理器，跟 Kirin 980、Snapdragon 855 一樣用 7nm 製程，咁佢效能又去到咩水平呢？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nNova 5 系列一共有三款手機，分別有 Nova 5、Nova 5i 以及 Nova 5 Pro，當中 Nova 5 及 Nova 5 Pro 規格、設計大致相同，Nova 5 用的是全新 Kirin 810 處理器，採用 7nm 製程、內置 A76 2.27GHz 雙核 + A55 1.88GHz 六核處理器、 Mali-G52 MP6 GPU 以及華為自家達芬奇 NPU，Antutu 測試成積達到 237437 分，比上代旗艦 Kirin 970 還要高。<br />\n<br />\n至於 Nova 5 Pro 則改配旗艦級的 Kirin 980 八核處理器，效能跟 Mate 20、P30 系列處於同一水平，另外還額外支援 NFC。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲ Kirin 810 的 Antutu 測試成積<br />\n <br />\n其餘規格方面，Nova 5 及 Nova 5 Pro 均配備 6.39 吋 FHD+ OLED 水滴全屏、內置支援 40W 快充的 3500mAh 電池。而拍攝方面則配備四攝相機，分別有 4800 萬像素主鏡頭 (Sony IMX586)、1600 萬像素超廣角、200 萬像素景深鏡頭以及 200 萬像素微距鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n售價方面，Nova 5 僅有 8+128 一個版本，賣人民幣 2799；Nova 5 Pro 則有 8+128 及 8+256 兩個版本，分別賣 人民幣 2999 / 3399 ，將於 7 月 13 日開賣。"},{"pid":"300fda0180ba4f18c2efe7df102d27f452639b32","tid":1253731,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ringhk.com/news2a.php?id=18754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ringhk.com%2Fnews2a.php%3Fid%3D18754&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr12vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=7ec6967a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ringhk.com/news2a.php?id=18754</a>"},{"pid":"87cd1a126321631a717f31eb68bfe0783f516836","tid":1253731,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f310f0f5c1e73fa16d6b36b8214a9607d72c6ba","tid":1253731,"uid":5846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"行紅星os？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97169667ebc72e3d6d391b932cbc29eb0d8f9bd0","tid":1253731,"uid":49664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"7nm 有機會 kirin  980低一個grade cpu"},{"pid":"5ac042d1cc0a8f7a4b4b28b23693c1e8f6c6f1df","tid":1253731,"uid":255744,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"8.20之前未達成和解，禁令先正式先效。今日6.24啫"},{"pid":"3ec2e677b930f8e0e54d3bfb23e8ed7cc35a4fb1","tid":1253731,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"最強中階cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e445b30995ea513c1198de6c0c2515ccde621ea","tid":1253731,"uid":18947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"Kirin cpu唔係唔好，不過佢隻gpu 我諗有生之年都追唔到snapdragon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4347cbe9a6149e617f5cc72ece2e7c0fe7a176","tid":1253731,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T23:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c99ca1fc7ebe7aab71738ae776b00d76d8c82e","tid":1253731,"uid":39550,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾，不值討論"},{"pid":"d02171cabce857214e6c44801ebd1115c5f8f292","tid":1253731,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"行咩os?"}]}